<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>A rectangular <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">altar</rs> (stained), with simple moulding above and below, worked on all four sides, with a relief of a <rs type="decoration">triple Hekate</rs> on the front face (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.14</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.28</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.20</measure>) . </p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs>  on the right side.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p>Rough; lunate <term lang="la">epsilon</term>, <term lang="la">sigma</term>, <term lang="la">omega</term>; unevenly aligned.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
 <head>Date</head>

<p>Perhaps <date exact="none" notAfter="0200" notBefore="0001" cert="low">first to second century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>).</p></div>

<div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
